#. Tag: keyword
#: index.docbook:26
#, no-c-format
msgid "<keyword>KDE</keyword>"
msgstr "<keyword>KDE</keyword>"

#. Tag: keyword
#: index.docbook:27
#, no-c-format
msgid "camera"
msgstr "kaamera"

#. Tag: keyword
#: index.docbook:28
#, no-c-format
msgid "photo"
msgstr "foto"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:32
#, no-c-format
msgid "This module allows you to configure support for your digital camera."
msgstr "See moodul võimaldab seadistada digitaalkaamera toetust."

#. Tag: guibutton
#: index.docbook:37
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guibutton>Add</guibutton>"
msgstr "<guibutton>Lisa</guibutton>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:39
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Click this button to select the camera's model and the port it is connected "
"to on your computer (&eg; USB, Serial). If your camera does not appear in "
"the list of <guilabel>Supported Cameras</guilabel>, go to the <ulink url="
"\"http://www.gphoto.org\">GPhoto web site</ulink> for a possible update."
msgstr ""
"Klõpsuga sellele nupule saab valida kaamera mudeli ja pordi, kuhu kaamera on "
"arvutis ühendatud (&eg; USB, jadaport). Kui kaamerat ei leidu nimekirjas "
"<guilabel>Toetatud kaamerad</guilabel>, tasuks uuendamiseks külastada <ulink "
"url=\"http://www.gphoto.org\">GPhoto veebilehekülge</ulink>."

#. Tag: guibutton
#: index.docbook:48
#, no-c-format
msgid "Test"
msgstr "Test"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:50
#, no-c-format
msgid "Click this button to test the connection to the selected camera."
msgstr "Valitud kaamera ühenduse testimiseks klõpsa seda nuppu."

#. Tag: guibutton
#: index.docbook:54
#, no-c-format
msgid "Remove"
msgstr "Eemalda"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:56
#, no-c-format
msgid "Removes the selected camera from the list."
msgstr "Eemaldab valitud kaamera nimekirjast."

#. Tag: guibutton
#: index.docbook:61
#, no-c-format
msgid "Configure"
msgstr "Seadista"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:63
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Click this button to change the configuration of the selected camera. The "
"availability of this feature and the contents of the Configuration dialog "
"depend on the camera model."
msgstr ""
"Klõpsuga sellele nupule saab muuta valitud kaamera seadistusi. Selle "
"võimaluse saadavus ning seadistustedialoogi sisu sõltub kaamera mudelist."

#. Tag: guibutton
#: index.docbook:69
#, no-c-format
msgid "Information"
msgstr "Info"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:71
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Click this button to view a summary of the current status of the selected "
"camera. The availability of this feature and the contents of the Information "
"dialog depend on the camera model."
msgstr ""
"Klõpsuga sellele nupule näeb valitud kaamera hetkeoleku kokkuvõtet. Selle "
"võimaluse saadavus ja teabedialoogi sisu sõltub kaamera mudelist."

#. Tag: guibutton
#: index.docbook:77
#, no-c-format
msgid "Cancel"
msgstr "Loobu"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:79
#, no-c-format
msgid "Click this button to cancel the current camera operation."
msgstr "Aktiivse kaameratoimingu katkestamiseks klõpsa seda nuppu."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:85
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "To view and download images from the digital camera, enter "
#| "<userinput>camera:/</userinput> in &konqueror;&apos;s location bar."
msgid ""
"To view and download images from the digital camera, enter "
"<userinput>camera:/</userinput> in &konqueror;&apos;s or &dolphin;&apos;s "
"location bar."
msgstr ""
"Digitaalkaamera piltide vaatamiseks ja nende allalaadimiseks kirjuta "
"&konqueror;i asukoharibale <userinput>camera:/</userinput>."

